Package oogasalad.editor.view

Class EditorComponentFactory

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.view.EditorComponentFactory
public class EditorComponentFactory extends Object
Factory class responsible for creating the main UI components of the Editor scene. Uses external configuration, delegates actions to the EditorController, and registers view components as listeners. (DESIGN-01, DESIGN-09: MVC, DESIGN-15, DESIGN-20: Factory Pattern, Observer Pattern)
Author:
Tatum McKinnis
